1524
01:52:19.770 --> 01:52:22.670
<i>♪ As I stand on
the precipice of death ♪</i>

1525
01:52:23.070 --> 01:52:25.700
<i>♪ My perspective is enormous ♪</i>

1526
01:52:26.370 --> 01:52:28.930
<i>♪ Every leaf, every cloud ♪</i>

1527
