<i>♪ Lead the marching band ♪</i>

1534
01:52:53.770 --> 01:52:58.260
<i>♪ Don't you let 'em fade ♪
♪ Your colors gray ♪</i>


1535
01:52:59.910 --> 01:53:02.540
<i>♪ 'Cause when all
is said and done ♪</i>

1536
01:53:03.080 --> 01:53:05.600
<i>♪ When youth is spent and burned ♪</i>

1537
01:53:06.480 --> 01:53:09.210
<i>♪ You'll see that it's all about ♪</i>

